EACopy provides CMake targets:

    find_package(EACopy CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE EACopy::EACopyLib)

EACopy is a high-performance file copy utility with delta compression capabilities.
It can be used as a library in your C++ projects for efficient file operations.

Key features:
- High-performance file copying
- Delta compression support
- Network acceleration
- Cross-platform compatibility (Windows primary)

For more information, visit: https://github.com/loonghao/EACopy
